{"data":[{"name":"80:1","price":"1. (நம் நபி) கடுகடுத்தார்; புறக்கணித்தார். (எதற்காக?)","arabic":"عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5759,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿabasa watawallā ","translations":["He frowned","and turned away","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿabasa","watawallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,790],[2,790,2185]]}},{"name":"80:2","price":"2. தன்னிடம் ஓர் பார்வையற்றவர் வந்ததற்காக. ","arabic":"أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلۡأَعۡمَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5760,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"an jāahu al-aʿmā ","translations":["Because","came to him","the blind man","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["an","jāahu","al-aʿmā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,3530],[3,3530,4575]]}},{"name":"80:3","price":"3. (நபியே! உம்மிடம் வந்த) அவர் பரிசுத்தவானாக இருக்கலாம் என்பதை நீர் அறிவீரா?","arabic":"وَمَا يُدۡرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُۥ يَزَّكَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5761,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā yud'rīka laʿallahu yazzakkā ","translations":["But what","would make you know","that he might","purify himself","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","yud'rīka","laʿallahu","yazzakkā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,700],[2,700,1770],[3,1770,2980],[4,2980,4465]]}},{"name":"80:4","price":"4. அல்லது அவர் நல்லுணர்வு பெறுவார். (உமது) நல்லுபதேசம் அவருக்குப் பயனளிக்கலாம் (என்பதை நீர் அறிவீரா? அவ்வாறிருக்க, அவரை நீர் ஏன் கடுகடுத்துப் புறக்கணித்தீர்?)","arabic":"أَوۡ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5762,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"aw yadhakkaru fatanfaʿahu al-dhik'rā ","translations":["Or","be reminded","so would benefit him","the reminder","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["aw","yadhakkaru","fatanfaʿahu","al-dhik'rā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,420],[2,420,1670],[3,1670,3590],[4,3590,5265]]}},{"name":"80:5","price":"5. (நபியே! மார்க்கத்தை) எவன் அலட்சியம் செய்கிறானோ,","arabic":"أَمَّا مَنِ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5763,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ammā mani is'taghnā ","translations":["As for","(him) who","considers himself free from need","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["ammā","mani","is'taghnā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1460],[2,1460,1850],[3,1850,2995]]}},{"name":"80:6","price":"6. அவனை வரவேற்பதில் நீர் அதிக சிரமத்தை எடுத்துக் கொள்கிறீர். ","arabic":"فَأَنتَ لَهُۥ تَصَدَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5764,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-anta lahu taṣaddā ","translations":["So you","to him","give attention","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-anta","lahu","taṣaddā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1500],[2,1500,2070],[3,2070,3385]]}},{"name":"80:7","price":"7. அவன் பரிசுத்தவானாக ஆகாவிட்டால் அதைப் பற்றி உம் மீது ஒரு குற்றமும் இல்லை(யே)!","arabic":"وَمَا عَلَيۡكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5765,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā ʿalayka allā yazzakkā ","translations":["And not","upon you","that not","he purifies himself","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","ʿalayka","allā","yazzakkā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1550],[3,1550,2450],[4,2450,3885]]}},{"name":"80:8","price":"8. எவர் (தானாகவே) உம்மிடம் ஓடி வருகிறாரோ,","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5766,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ammā man jāaka yasʿā ","translations":["But as for","(he) who","came to you","striving","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ammā","man","jāaka","yasʿā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1740],[2,1740,2860],[3,2860,5010],[4,5010,6085]]}},{"name":"80:9","price":"9. அவர்தான் (அல்லாஹ்வுக்குப்) பயப்படுகிறவர்.","arabic":"وَهُوَ يَخۡشَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5767,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wahuwa yakhshā ","translations":["While he","fears","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["wahuwa","yakhshā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,1635]]}},{"name":"80:10","price":"10. எனினும், நீர் அவரை அலட்சியம் செய்து விடுகிறீர்.","arabic":"فَأَنتَ عَنۡهُ تَلَهَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5768,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-anta ʿanhu talahhā ","translations":["But you","from him","(are) distracted","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-anta","ʿanhu","talahhā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1310],[2,1310,1940],[3,1940,3135]]}},{"name":"80:11","price":"11. அவ்வாறு செய்யாதீர். (திரு குர்ஆனாகிய) இது ஒரு நல்லுபதேசம்தான்.","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذۡكِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5769,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā innahā tadhkiratun ","translations":["Nay","Indeed, it","(is) a reminder","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","innahā","tadhkiratun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2699],[2,2699,4269],[3,4269,5804]]}},{"name":"80:12","price":"12. எவர் (நேரான வழியில் செல்ல) விரும்புகிறாரோ அவர் இதை(ச் செவியுற்று) ஞாபகத்தில் வைத்துக் கொள்வார்.","arabic":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5770,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"faman shāa dhakarahu ","translations":["So whosoever","wills","may remember it","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["faman","shāa","dhakarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,940],[2,940,3370],[3,3370,4535]]}},{"name":"80:13","price":"13. இது (லவ்ஹுல் மஹ்ஃபூள் என்னும்) மிக்க கண்ணியமான புத்தகத்தில் (வரையப்பட்டுள்ளது);","arabic":"فِي صُحُفٖ مُّكَرَّمَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5771,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fī ṣuḥufin mukarramatin ","translations":["In","sheets","honored","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["fī","ṣuḥufin","mukarramatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,430],[2,430,1160],[3,1160,3425]]}},{"name":"80:14","price":"14. உயர்வுமிக்க தூய்மையான இடத்தில் வைக்கப்பட்டுள்ளது; (அது) மிகப் பரிசுத்தமானது.","arabic":"مَّرۡفُوعَةٖ مُّطَهَّرَةِۭ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5772,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"marfūʿatin muṭahharatin ","translations":["Exalted","purified","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["marfūʿatin","muṭahharatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,3795]]}},{"name":"80:15","price":"15. எழுதுபவர்களின் கைகளினால் (வரையப்பட்டது).","arabic":"بِأَيۡدِي سَفَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5773,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"bi-aydī safaratin ","translations":["In (the) hands","(of) scribes","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["bi-aydī","safaratin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1010],[2,1010,2125]]}},{"name":"80:16","price":"16. (அவர்கள்) மிக கண்ணியமானவர்கள், மிக நல்லவர்கள்.","arabic":"كِرَامِۭ بَرَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5774,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"kirāmin bararatin ","translations":["Noble","dutiful","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["kirāmin","bararatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1520],[2,1520,2785]]}},{"name":"80:17","price":"17. (பாவம் செய்யும்) மனிதனுக்குக் கேடுதான். அவன் எவ்வளவு நன்றிகெட்டவனாக இருக்கிறான்.","arabic":"قُتِلَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَآ أَكۡفَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5775,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"qutila al-insānu mā akfarahu ","translations":["Is destroyed","[the] man","how","ungrateful is he","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["qutila","al-insānu","mā","akfarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,570],[2,570,2770],[3,2770,4540],[4,4540,5905]]}},{"name":"80:18","price":"18. எதைக்கொண்டு (இறைவன்) அவனைப் படைத்திருக்கிறான் (என்பதை அவன் கவனித்தானா)?","arabic":"مِنۡ أَيِّ شَيۡءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5776,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"min ayyi shayin khalaqahu ","translations":["From","what","thing","He created him","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["min","ayyi","shayin","khalaqahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,460],[2,460,1070],[3,1070,1940],[4,1940,3225]]}},{"name":"80:19","price":"19. ஒரு துளி இந்திரியத்தைக் கொண்டுதான் அவன் அவனைப் படைக்கிறான். (அவன் இருக்கின்ற இவ்வாறே, அவனை மனிதனாக அமைத்து) அவனுக்குச் சக்தியைக் கொடுத்தான்.","arabic":"مِن نُّطۡفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ فَقَدَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5777,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"min nuṭ'fatin khalaqahu faqaddarahu ","translations":["From","a semen-drop","He created him","then He proportioned him","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["min","nuṭ'fatin","khalaqahu","faqaddarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,340],[2,340,2500],[3,2500,3560],[4,3560,5325]]}},{"name":"80:20","price":"20. பின்னர், அவன் செய்யக்கூடிய (நன்மை தீமைக்குரிய) வழியை அவனுக்கு எளிதாக்கி வைத்தான்.","arabic":"ثُمَّ ٱلسَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5778,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma al-sabīla yassarahu ","translations":["Then","the way","He made easy for him","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","al-sabīla","yassarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1350],[2,1350,2530],[3,2530,4055]]}},{"name":"80:21","price":"21. பின்னர், அவனை மரணிக்கச் செய்து சமாதியில் புகுத்துகிறான்.","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُۥ فَأَقۡبَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5779,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma amātahu fa-aqbarahu ","translations":["Then","He causes him to die","and provides a grave for him","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","amātahu","fa-aqbarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1240],[2,1240,2640],[3,2640,4435]]}},{"name":"80:22","price":"22. பின்னர் (அவன் விரும்பியபொழுது உயிர் கொடுத்து) அவனே அவனை உயிர்ப்பிப்பான்.","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِذَا شَآءَ أَنشَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5780,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma idhā shāa ansharahu ","translations":["Then","when","He wills","He will resurrect him","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","idhā","shāa","ansharahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1470],[2,1470,2070],[3,2070,4340],[4,4340,6435]]}},{"name":"80:23","price":"23. எனினும், நிச்சயமாக மனிதன் இறைவனுடைய கட்டளையை நிறைவேற்றுவதில்லை.","arabic":"كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقۡضِ مَآ أَمَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5781,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā lammā yaqḍi mā amarahu ","translations":["Nay","Not","he has accomplished","what","He commanded him","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","lammā","yaqḍi","mā","amarahu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,920],[2,920,2410],[3,2410,3170],[4,3170,5100],[5,5100,6435]]}},{"name":"80:24","price":"24. மனிதன் தன் உணவை (அது எங்கிருந்து எவ்வாறு வருகிறது என்பதைச்) சிறிது கவனித்துப் பார்க்கவும்.","arabic":"فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِۦٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5782,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"falyanẓuri al-insānu ilā ṭaʿāmihi ","translations":["Then let look","the man","at","his food","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["falyanẓuri","al-insānu","ilā","ṭaʿāmihi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1990],[2,1990,3930],[3,3930,4510],[4,4510,6185]]}},{"name":"80:25","price":"25. நிச்சயமாக நாமே ஏராளமான மழையை பொழியச் செய்தோம்,","arabic":"أَنَّا صَبَبۡنَا ٱلۡمَآءَ صَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5783,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"annā ṣababnā al-māa ṣabban ","translations":["That [We]","[We] poured","the water","(in) abundance","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["annā","ṣababnā","al-māa","ṣabban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1620],[2,1620,2530],[3,2530,4850],[4,4850,5935]]}},{"name":"80:26","price":"26. பின்னர், பூமியையும் பிளந்(து வெடிக்கச் செய்)தோம்.","arabic":"ثُمَّ شَقَقۡنَا ٱلۡأَرۡضَ شَقّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5784,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"thumma shaqaqnā al-arḍa shaqqan ","translations":["Then","We cleaved","the earth","splitting","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["thumma","shaqaqnā","al-arḍa","shaqqan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1630],[2,1630,2520],[3,2520,3410],[4,3410,4735]]}},{"name":"80:27","price":"27. பின்னர், அதிலிருந்து வித்துக்களை முளைத்து வளரும்படி செய்கிறோம்.","arabic":"فَأَنۢبَتۡنَا فِيهَا حَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5785,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-anbatnā fīhā ḥabban ","translations":["Then We caused to grow","therein","grain","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-anbatnā","fīhā","ḥabban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2290],[2,2290,3190],[3,3190,4245]]}},{"name":"80:28","price":"28. (இவ்வாறு) திராட்சைக் கனிகளையும் மற்ற காய்கறிகளையும்,","arabic":"وَعِنَبٗا وَقَضۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5786,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"waʿinaban waqaḍban ","translations":["And grapes","and green fodder","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["waʿinaban","waqaḍban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1420],[2,1420,3125]]}},{"name":"80:29","price":"29. ஜைத்தூனையும், பேரீச்சை மரத்தையும்,","arabic":"وَزَيۡتُونٗا وَنَخۡلٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5787,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wazaytūnan wanakhlan ","translations":["And olive","and date-palms","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["wazaytūnan","wanakhl